## 11. Applications

* Smart Homes
* Building Automation
* Security Systems
* Energy Management Systems
* IoT Control Platforms

## 12. Conclusion

The project successfully demonstrates RTL design, verification, synthesis, and automation control using Verilog HDL. The design is FPGA-ready and can be extended with IoT communication, UART, MQTT, and sensor interfaces.

